oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Man taking bass fish from Harpeth River, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of unidentified man taking bass from the Harpeth River, Tenn. Man is standing on riverbank with fishing pole, basket and wearing a hat, shirt and pants. Man is smoking a pipe. In the background, the river, bank and trees are visible.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
